text: Jaroslav Mikoška (born 21 December 1933) is a Czech gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zlín
